NAME
    sleep - delay for a specified amount of time

SYNOPSIS
    sleep DURATION

DESCRIPTION
    Pauses execution for the specified duration.

    Duration can be specified as:
    - 5 or 5s   - 5 seconds
    - 500ms     - 500 milliseconds
    - 1m        - 1 minute
    - 1h        - 1 hour

    Maximum duration is capped at 1 hour.

EXAMPLES
    sleep 5
        Pause for 5 seconds

    sleep 500ms
        Pause for half a second

    sleep 1m
        Pause for 1 minute

    sleep 30 &
        Sleep in background

SEE ALSO
    timeout, jobs
